Writing Build Scripts

https://docs.gradle.org/current/userguide/writing_build_scripts.html


Build Script Blocks

    - SourceSet: https://docs.gradle.org/current/dsl/org.gradle.api.tasks.SourceSet.html

        - It represents a logical group of Java source and resource files
        - Covered in more details in
            - https://docs.gradle.org/current/userguide/building_java_projects.html#sec:java_source_sets

structure:

sourceSets {
    // properties
    main {
        // configure the java source for this set
        java {

        }
    }
}


Task Types

Exec:
https://docs.gradle.org/current/dsl/org.gradle.api.tasks.Exec.html